urdu transliteration text:
Zainab lipat ke roi, Abbas key Nishaan seAisa Ghayur bhaiya, Laaungi phir kahan se
Zainab held the Alam of Abbas and wept,
@HujjatELC

Ek baar tum chacha jaan, Khaimo mei lout aawoShikwa na phir sunoge, Paani ka is zubaan se,Aisa Ghayur bhaiya, Laaungi phir kahan se
Uncle Abbas, please return to the tents just once more,
@HujjatELC
